title: Underwater Tomb of the Shadows
story: For decades the tomb remained uninhabited. Lately a gang of bandits rediscovered it. The tomb is home to a valuable specie of plants.

notes.text: A great ironclad gate with a keyhole on the western wall.
A stuffed halfling with an uncanny, covered with carvings scarf in their hands.
Some gold and a chainmail among rubble on the ground.
A mutilated body of a bandit, a weird, unnaturally heavy spear close to it.
